--- When the callback returns a Deferred, the result is flattened.
--- @generic S, F, V
--- @param success (fun(value: S): Deferred<V,F>)? Callback that returns a Deferred
--- @param failure (fun(reason: F): Deferred<V,F>)?
--- @return Deferred<V,F>
